{"tid":1599750,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"喺俄羅斯大大力屌鳩兩隻支那臭雞","createTime":"2019-09-28T07:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:21:18.000Z","uid":141782,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd64eae1f7a04c25de8fa9d07ee78426ff4fef92","tid":1599750,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"喺gum 行緊<br />\n有兩隻支那臭雞用支那話：哎 那個<br />\n我望都唔撚望行咗去<br />\n條臭雞唔撚識死仲過黎話唉你神經病呀<br />\n屌佢老尾我用英文屌佢去外國唔識講俄文都講英文，唉你老尾，英文都唔識講唔該你go back to your country, 呢度係俄羅斯你咪撚同我講chinese<br />\n兩條臭雞擘大口呆撚咗企喺度聽咗我講幾分鐘<br />\n我諗佢地一句都唔識聽不過我屌得好撚爽快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗幾時冚國鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w439nv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw439nv6.jpg&h=22796fef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea43f3a4b75771fa65cdc8e9b223ea13dde2322","tid":1599750,"uid":144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"下次講 Cyka blyat idi nahui<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢句我諗個個都識"},{"pid":"2df873aa9cc5fbd5a51f1e7c33e70e7c313cd1c4","tid":1599750,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"СУКА <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25c493f58652b322cdcfa20e4519398adf093cb","tid":1599750,"uid":141782,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"發覺次次旅行都有個行程係同支那賤種開片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46c51fa6221908add7946fc418637b734cb238c","tid":1599750,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"絲打好波"},{"pid":"ab88eeb7b13113cf0ea201c12f3497163182187c","tid":1599750,"uid":105905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a25c493f58652b322cdcfa20e4519398adf093cb","tid":159975